  80,31,Wa Fākihatan Wa 'Abbāan
  80,32,Matā`āan Lakum Wa Li'an`āmikum
  80,33,Fa'idhā Jā'ati Aş-Şākhkhahu
  80,34,Yawma Yafirru Al-Mar'u Min 'Akhīhi
